<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4677108>
    dc:description "Figures 2–9. Paroniella blanchardi (Parona, 1897). (2) scolex, dorsoventral view; (3) rostellar hook; (4) sucker spines; (5) Anterior extremity of strobila showing reticulated osmoregulatory system; (6) scolex, apical view; (7) optical transverse section of hand-cut section showing longitudinal and transverse musculature; (8) mature segment; (9) gravid segment. Scale bars: Figs. 5, 8, 9—1.0 mm; Figs. 2, 6, 7—0.1, mm; Figs. 3, 4, to same scale—0.01 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4677108/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

